{"TopicId":139000,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"How to Be Evil!","CreatedByName":"EliasDanger","CreatedById":151803,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-05T00:33:36Z","PageNum":9,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Omegagoldfish","CreatedById":161373,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T18:31:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2/10 not specified to explode when touched.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI set an orphanage on fire because they were having their annual Christmas song-and-dance routine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GDJ","CreatedById":58462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T18:38:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751165\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139000\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473618706\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161373\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Omegagoldfish\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Omegagoldfish said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI set an orphanage on fire because they were having their annual Christmas song-and-dance routine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00220000dbc618c626656b543e4ac40f834d.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/00/00/db/0000dbc618c626656b543e4ac40f834d.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Omegagoldfish","CreatedById":161373,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T18:40:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMislabeling things is the best.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022enhanced-buzz-29828-1376411831-6.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://img.buzzfeed.com/buzzfeed-static/static/enhanced/webdr03/2013/8/13/12/enhanced-buzz-29828-1376411831-6.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s funny is that it really does explode when you pull the trigger.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-11T18:41:01Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2016 06:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Omegagoldfish\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GDJ","CreatedById":58462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T18:42:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, what would be evil\u00A0is the extinguisher refilled with Nitrous Oxide.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe victims die laughing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-11T18:42:57Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2016 06:42  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by GDJ\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Omegagoldfish","CreatedById":161373,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T18:43:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222751186\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139000\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473619326\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GDJ\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, GDJ said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, what would be funny is the extinguisher refilled with NO2.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe victims die laughing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not pure oxygen? Nice refreshing breeze, anyone?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003EAlso can someone rate the other two things I made?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-11T18:44:01Z\u0022 title=\u002209/11/2016 06:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 11, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Omegagoldfish\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GDJ","CreatedById":58462,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T18:51:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh sorry.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n7/10 for both. I\u0027d use them (if I was a raging Psychopath that is...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dark Junior","CreatedById":102999,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T20:43:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0/10 No evil\u003Cbr\u003E\nThink about your tongue\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpannerMonkey(smce)","CreatedById":50907,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-11T20:58:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe ultimate marine engineers evil, wait patiently until your buddy has finished his latest engine rebuild, comment on how good it looks, and the moment he turns his back just place a valve cotter tucked up against the sump,( this little part if not fitted has the possibility of completely wrecking an engine) and quietly walk away, some sort time later the air will fill with obscenities as your buddy proceeds to strip the top off the recently rebuilt engine just to make sure he has fitted them all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022khvIrch.jpg?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/khvIrch.jpg?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"0