114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T02:49:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6/10 Evil, but pointless.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI start a drug cartel based out of Russia that uses cold-war MIRV ICBMs to distribute the product around the world.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd incite nuclear war when the US thinks that Russia just shot a nuke at them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGet rich AND start a nuclear holocaust!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-12T02:50:04Z\u0022 title=\u002209/12/2016 02:50  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 12, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by njmksr\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TopHeavy11","CreatedById":154744,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T11:28:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n10/10\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://tse3.mm.bing.net/th?id=OIP.Mc49b693061f748cc6f8e0ef6bd3e109bH0\u0026amp;pid=15.1\u0026amp;P=0\u0026amp;w=287\u0026amp;h=163\u0022 style=\u0022width:500px;height:282px;\u0022 alt=\u0022th?id=OIP.Mc49b693061f748cc6f8e0ef6bd3e109bH0\u0026amp;pid=15.1\u0026amp;P=0\u0026amp;w=287\u0026amp;h=163\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI unite every villain from across the multiverse, rebootverse, and spoofverse, and tell them their target is every inhabited planet, starting with Earth.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dark Junior","CreatedById":102999,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T15:23:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5/10 Been there, done that.\u003Cbr\u003E\nI make you...\u003Cbr\u003E\nA. Think about your tongue.\u003Cbr\u003E\nB. Only capable of saying \u0022Welcome to Corneria!\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T16:24:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to Corneria!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yPYZpwSpKmA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThis is the universe\u0027s soundtrack now.\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Omegagoldfish","CreatedById":161373,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T18:49:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou sadistic monster. I love you. 7/10\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nApply invisible ink to everything, and giggle uncontrollably at messages only I can see. Then make them all visible when people get used to the laughter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T21:23:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3/10 Just annoying and funny, but can ruin some stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hack every TV channel and rickroll everyone watching the channel at fully random times.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy am I into rickrolling this much right not? I don\u0027t get it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"njmksr","CreatedById":114236,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-12T21:46:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n10/10 I don\u0027t mind Never Gonna Give You Up\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBrainwash the cities of New York, LA, Boston, San Francisco, etc. into thinking that the floor really is lava\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBtw Hi \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161373-omegagoldfish/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161373\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161373-omegagoldfish/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Omegagoldfish\u003C/a\u003E!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0